trans-unit.source: Account not yet activated please check your email first or request an additional activation code.

trans-unit.source: Activation sent to address provided. Please check your e-mail to activate your account which will complete your registration.

trans-unit.source: User with this name already exists please choose another.

trans-unit.source: E-mail address changed and activation e-mail sent to reactivate account.

trans-unit.source: E-mail already in use please login with existing credentials.
trans-unit.target: E-pošte već se koristi molim prijava sa postojeće vjerodajnice.

trans-unit.source: Password must be at least 8 characters.

trans-unit.source: Password already reset or process not initiated.
